  <summary date="2015-04-16T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Small Business Tax Equity Act of 2015

Amends the Internal Revenue Code to exempt a trade or business that conducts marijuana sales in compliance with state law from the prohibition against allowing business-related tax credits or deductions for expenditures in connection with trafficking in controlled substances.</summary>
